<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification Successful</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333; /* --text-color-dark approximation */
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f0f8ff; /* --bg-main */
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #10b981; /* Success color */
        color: #ffffff; /* White text */
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        border: 1px solid #ccebff; /* Lighter shade derived from --border-color */
        border-top: none;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280; /* --muted-foreground approximation */
      }
      .success-icon {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 60px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #10b981; /* Success color */
      }
      .button {
        display: block;
        background-color: #10b981; /* Success color */
        color: #ffffff !important; /* White text, !important */
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        width: 200px;
        border: none;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #059669; /* Darker success color */
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      a {
        /* Standard link color */
        color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Email Verification Successful!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>

      <div class="success-icon">✓</div>

      <p>
        Your email address has been successfully verified. Thank you for
        completing this step!
      </p>

      <p>You now have full access to all features of UniNav, including:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Uploading and downloading study materials</li>
        <li>Creating and saving collections</li>
        <li>Participating in the UniNav community</li>
        <li>Access to department-specific resources</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Ready to get started with UniNav?</p>

      <a
        href="https://uninav.com/dashboard"
        class="button"
        style="color: #ffffff !important"
        >Go to Dashboard</a
      >

      <p>We're excited to have you as part of our academic community!</p>
      <p>The UniNav Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UniNav. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
